==Recipes==
Wool is not used in any recipes.

==Tailoring==
Wool is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a [[Tailoring|Plain Shirt]].
*Male version: [[File:Shirt038.png|24px]]
*Female version: [[File:Shirt041.png|24px]]
It is a white dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed.

==Quests==
*Wool may be randomly requested during any season at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|1020}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.  Wool will never be requested unless you own a [[Rabbit]] or [[Sheep]].

==History==
{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}
{{History|1.1|Increased value from 270g to 340g}}
{{History|1.4|Add chance for double cloth from loom for quality wool.  Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}

